好成熟 知道自己做緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n無論有幾hurt 自己都中個頭埋去 真係好愛佢"},{"pid":"47513f0ebbcf4bd40c89af543a093e55f64102b8","tid":435204,"uid":146642,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T05:22:47.000Z","msg":"一齊左5年 好唔捨得 分左手最好delete曬所有野  唔係既話會成日諗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n初初分手個人好頹 夜晚又聽埋啲分手情歌 個心痛左1年  依家已經有第2春"},{"pid":"80157f14930592feb94ea601f7ff8d613521129b","tid":435204,"uid":89505,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T05:23:32.000Z","msg":"始終相信 真係愛你既唔會走<br />\n等於你重新睇一本已經睇過既書 明知結局係點 仲期待啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拍左三年 分手後用盡方法挽留 到佢想翻轉頭 發現一切已經翻唔到之前咁<br />\n愛一個唔愛你嘅人 太辛苦 何必去屈委自己 愛得咁辛苦 放手都係一種愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3782d0b79f99d36e83430418e4ee9d88ca14fb87","tid":435204,"uid":152342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T05:28:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>始終相信 真係愛你既唔會走<br />\n等於你重新睇一本已經睇過既書 明知結局係點 仲期待啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拍左三年 分手後用盡方法挽留 到佢想翻轉頭 發現一切已經翻唔到之前咁<br />\n愛一個唔愛你嘅人 太辛苦 何必去屈委自己 愛得咁辛苦 放手都係一種愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f52893d9d0f44aad747efad808cb6e2f7dc28eb","tid":435204,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T05:29:00.000Z","msg":"總之我會等囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\"